quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,Dil khush kun chalti hawaon ki qasam
  77,2,Phir zor say jhonka denay walion ki qasam
  77,3,Phir(abar ko) ubhaar ker peraganda kernay waliyon ki qasam
  77,4,Phir haq o batil ko joda joda kerdenay walay
  77,5,Aur wahee laanay walay farishton ki qasam
  77,6,Jo (wahee) ilzaam utarnay ya aggah kerdenay kay liey hoti hai
  77,7,Jiss cheez ka tum saywada kiya jata hai wo yaqeenan honay wali hai
  77,8,Pus jab sitary be nor kerdiey jaeingay
  77,9,Aur jab aasman tor phor diya jaey ga
  77,10,Aur jab pahar tukray tukray kerdkay ura diya jaeyga
  77,11,Aur jab rasoolon ko waqat muqarrara per laya jaeyga
  77,12,Kiss din kay liey (in sab ko)mo akkhir kiya gaya hai
  77,13,Faislay kay din kay liey
  77,14,Aur tujhay kiya maloom kay faislay ka din kiya hai
  77,15,Uss din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
  77,16,Kiya hum ney aglon ko halak nahi kiya
  77,17,Phir hum inkay baad peechlon ko laey
  77,18,Hum gunehgaron kay sath issi tarah kertay hein
  77,19,Uss din jhutlanay walon kay liey wail(afsos) hai
  77,20,Kiya hum ney tumhein haqeer paani say(money say) peda nahi kiya
  77,21,Phir hum ney ussay mazboot o mehfooz jaga mein rakha
  77,22,Aik muqarrara waqat tak
  77,23,Phir hum ney andaza kiya aur hum kiya khoob andaza kernay walay hein
  77,24,Uss din takzeeb kernay walon ki kharabi hai
  77,25,KIya hum ney zameen ko sametnay wali nahi banaya
  77,26,Zindon ko bhi aur murdon ko bhi
  77,27,Aur hum ney iss mein buland o bhar pahar bana diey aur tum hein seraab kernay wala meetha paani pilaya
  77,28,Uss din jhoot jannay walon kay liey waaye aur afsos hai
  77,29,Uss dozakh ki taraf jao jissay tum jhutlatay rahey thay
  77,30,Chalo teen shakhon waly saaye ki taraf
  77,31,Jo dar asel na saaye denay wala hai aur na sholay say bacha sakhta hai
  77,32,yaqeenan dozakh chingariyan phenkti hai jo misil mehal kay hein
  77,33,Goya kay who zard unt hain
  77,34,Aaj in jhot jannay walon ki durgat hai
  77,35,Aaj (ka din)wo din hai yeh bol bhi na sakein gay
  77,36,Na unhen maazrat ki ijazat di jaeygi
  77,37,Uss din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
  77,38,Yeh hai faislay ka din hum ney tumhein aur aglon ko sab ko jama kerliya hai
  77,39,Pus agar tum mujh say koi chaal chal saktay hoto chal lo
  77,40,Waaye hai uss din jhutlanay walon kay liey